[h1]Spawn Point Tool[/h1]

Place personal respawn points with the Toolgun.

Use it for building sessions, map testing, sandbox checkpoints, or any server where players need simple personal spawn control without changing gamemodes.

[h2]Quick Start[/h2]
[list]
[*]Open the Toolgun menu and select [b]Spawn Point Tool[/b].
[*][b]Left-click[/b] a surface to add a respawn point.
[*][b]Right-click[/b] near a marker to remove it.
[*][b]Reload[/b] to clear your points on the current map.
[/list]

[h2]Highlights[/h2]
[list]
[*]Each player manages their own respawn points.
[*]Place one checkpoint or several random respawn choices.
[*]Respawns keep the direction you were facing when placed.
[*]Optional saving across sessions.
[*]Live placement preview and in-world markers.
[*]Optional checks for blocked or dangerous respawn points.
[/list]

[h2]Settings Menu[/h2]
[list]
[*]Toggle your custom respawns without deleting saved points.
[*]Choose whether points persist across sessions.
[*]Show synced markers without holding the tool.
[*]Delete current-map points or all saved points from the menu.
[/list]

[h2]Admin Controls[/h2]
[list]
[*]Enable or disable custom respawns server-wide.
[*]Set the maximum points each player can place.
[*]Adjust remove radius and spawn surface offset.
[*]Choose marker visibility: private, admins only, or everyone.
[*]Configure danger checks and stricter respawn hull checks.
[/list]

[h2]Compatibility[/h2]
[list]
[*]Should be compatible with pretty much everything, and if not, let me know and I can add it. 
[/list]

[h2]Support[/h2]
[list]
[*][url=https://github.com/DeisDev/SpawnPointTool]GitHub repository[/url]
[*][url=https://github.com/DeisDev/SpawnPointTool/issues/new/choose]Report an issue[/url]
[/list]

When reporting a problem, include the addon version, map, gamemode, other spawn-related addons, console errors, and steps to reproduce it.

